chat_history.content:
Here is a list of the four most-subscribed YouTube channels, based on my latest information:

1. T-Series
2. Cocomelon
3. SET India
4. MrBeast

T-Series was founded in 2013. Cocomelon began in 2006 and is the third-most-viewed channel on YouTube. SET India's exact start date is unclear, but it was launched in 2015. MrBeast, on the other hand, was started in 2012.
